{"tid":2050201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日部份悼念六四活動地點時間","createTime":"2020-06-04T03:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T08:19:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9eec81c1f0d7c18f9419053deafce41bd6fb2c34","tid":2050201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"今日部份悼念六四活動地點時間<br />\n<br />\n地點時間以圖內為準<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UASSMEQ5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUASSMEQ5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE.gif&h=c118adaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島 晚上7:00至8:30 西營盤港鐵站般成道C出口<br />\n<br />\n黄埔海濱 下午3:00 至晚上8:00街站<br />\n晚上8:00至10:00 默哀及「抉擇時刻.燃點黑暗」放映會<br />\n<br />\n旺 角 晚上8:00 朗豪坊雕塑對出空地<br />\n<br />\n觀 塘 晚上8:00 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n<br />\n荃 灣 晚上8:00西樓角花園、千色店行人天橋、荃灣廣場出對空地、愉景新城巴士總站、荃新天地行人天橋、梨木樹邨商場出對等<br />\n<br />\n葵 青 下午5:00 葵涌廣場側空地、大窩口港鐵站B出口、賢麗商場外<br />\n晚上7:00 青衣泳永池外、長宏巴士總站青衣連儂牆、青衣碼頭等<br />\n晚上7:30 石籬商場外圍<br />\n<br />\n沙田 晚上8:00大圍港鐵站A出口、馬鞍山公園出對海濱<br />\n<br />\n屯 門 晚上7:30 屯門公園<br />\n<br />\n離島 下午4時至7時南丫島榕樹灣大街<br />\n<br />\n資料來源:網上平台「香港人日程表」<br />\n<br />\n地點時間以圖內為準<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UASSMEQ5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUASSMEQ5NEQ62DSTACK7H73SDE.gif&h=c118adaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e89a6dd151e4bf475fd226177cf543ecf0b2ec74","tid":2050201,"uid":159818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"唔係全世界維園咩？"},{"pid":"8accc0c3b474ca50ad78c6e0e094297f47ab1427","tid":2050201,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"又話要影靚相？"},{"pid":"9384a7f74a67f906f4b562289c2dcf9f2f5f6e15","tid":2050201,"uid":25558,"like":0,